title: Chiang Mai, Heaven or Hell? (Tourist Destination Review)
description:
Paradise for some.  :-/  On Patreon you'll get the full video, and a bunch of other exclusive content: I'm increasingly recording Patreon-only podcasts (due to the difficulty of uploading video in Asia/China).  You'll also get to cross paths with other vegans who are serious about getting organized for social activism.  Currently (June 6, 2016), I'm taking questions (from subscribers) for a Q&A session. https://www.patreon.com/a_bas_le_ciel

This video is a conversation about the reality of Chiang Mai, Thailand, in 2016 (in contrasts to what some tourists might be expecting).
